text: 9.1 No Consequential or Indirect Damages. NEITHER PARTY SHALL BE LIABLE UNDER OR IN CONNECTION WITH THIS AGREEMENT FOR
INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, LIQUIDATED, SPECIAL OR EXEMPLARY DAMAGES OR PENALTIES, INCLUDING WITHOUT
LIMITATION. LOSSES OF BUSINESS. REVENUE OR ANTICIPATED PROFITS. REGARDLESS OF WHETHER SUCH DAMAGE WAS
FORESEEABLE AND WHETHER LICENSOR HAS BEEN ADVISED OF THE POSSIBILITY OF SUCH DAMAGES
